article.headline: Pruitt scores 19, Lipscomb downs UNC Asheville 86-75
article.description: — Will Pruitt had 19 points in Lipscomb's 86-75 win against UNC Asheville on Friday in the Northern Classic.
article.linkText: Pruitt scores 19, Lipscomb downs UNC Asheville 86-75
article.story: MONTREAL -- — Will Pruitt had 19 points in Lipscomb's 86-75 win against UNC Asheville on Friday in the Northern Classic. Pruitt had six rebounds for the Bisons (4-2). Owen McCormack scored 18 points and added 10 rebounds. Derrin Boyd was 4 of 11 shooting and 9 of 10 from the free throw line to finish with 18 points, while adding six rebounds. Drew Pember led the Bulldogs (2-3) in scoring, finishing with 28 points and two blocks. Josh Banks added 20 points and eight rebounds for UNC Asheville. Jamon Battle also recorded 11 points, seven rebounds and two steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
